Comments_List: Through listening to a wide breadth of speakers discuss their latest research programs, I got a sense of the types of questions psychologists of all stages of their careers are exploring, as well as inspiration for new lines of inquiry in my own endeavors.

Yes! Current works was very enriching. Some of the talks can veer on the technical side, but as far a series of psychology lectures goes, I think they would be relatively accessible for people who don't have strong psyc backgrounds.
